nlattice, we obtain a new Yang-Baxter map of the NLS type, which can be\nconsidered as a fully discrete analog of the principal chiral model for\nprojection matrices.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 29 May 2015 05:16:36 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 19 Jun 2015 19:44:36 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 18 Aug 2015 19:35:20 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-08-19"}
