a}$ illustrate how the ferromagnetism originates\nand also how one can keep this cubic perovskite robustly ferromagnetic far\nabove the room temperature.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 29 May 2015 06:59:26 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-01-20"}
