ns on the inclined surfaces, which permits one to etch well-defined\nmonolithic 3D nanostructures.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 29 May 2015 13:34:09 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 1 Jun 2015 13:35:35 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 29 Jun 2015 09:56:29 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-09-08"}
